a\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b LP\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Michael Heseltine, one of the earliest champions of building the much-criticised Millennium Dome, would "take the same decision again".\par \par \uc2 Mr Heseltine said he remained convinced it had been right to mark the millennium in a comparable way to the 1851 Great Exhibition and the 1951 Festival of Britain. And it had been right to respond to the regeneration needs of the Greenwich peninsula where the Dome was built.\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b TD\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 "Of course, with hindsight things should have been done differently," Mr Heseltine said. "We should have appointed a great impresario from day one. We did not have the right legislative powers, and had to work within the framework that existed."\par \par \uc2 He was speaking before yesterday's launch of Regeneration &Renewal, a weekly magazine from Haymarket Business Publications, part of the publishing organisation of which Mr Heseltine is chairman.\par \par \uc2 The magazine has been produced in response to a growing interest in regeneration.\par \par \uc2 The government's comprehensive spending review this year means that public funding for regeneration projects is about to grow substantially.\par \par \uc2 Mr Heseltine, who was \b \highlight22\uc2 environment\b0 \highlight\uc2  secretary twice in Conservative governments, was responsible for many of the approaches to urban renewal adopted during the 1980s and 1990s. These included urban development corporations and City Challenge, under which local authorities had to bid for funding.\par \par \uc2 "There is still a huge amount to be done, but we succeeded in showing how appropriate use of public money to pump-prime projects can lever in far larger levels of private sector resource," he said.\par \par \uc2 Public financial support was needed to initiate regeneration projects, and there had to be "a profit element at the end of the journey" to attract the private sector, Mr Heseltine said.\par \par \uc2 More limited \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2  programmes in regeneration areas were "beneficial and benign, but are never going to be a source of serious money". \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b CO\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 newmxc : \uc2 New Millennium Experience Co\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b NS\b0\cell \pard