0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b LP\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 The Small Business Service will help smaller companies to become active in the community under a package of government initiatives to develop \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2  announced yesterday.\par \par \uc2 Businesses were "inextricably linked" with the communities they served, said Kim Howells, minister for \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2 . Mr Howells yesterday published a Department of Trade and Industry report setting out priorities for encouraging companies to become involved in local communities.\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b TD\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 In addition to using the SBS to help extend social responsibility programmes to more companies, the government intends to encourage social enterprise in deprived communities. Help in regenerating deprived areas and improving literacy and numeracy skills are priorities on which it wants the private sector to focus more of its community effort.\par \par \uc2 The DTI report said the business case for \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2  was strengthening as the \b \highlight22\uc2 environment\b0 \highlight\uc2  in which companies operated became "more sensitive to social, ethical and environmental performance".\par \par \uc2 A European Commission green paper on \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2 , in which the UK government is closely involved, is planned. Today the government will launch a website giving examples of good practice and seeking views on the future direction of social responsibility policy.\par \par \uc2 The government has reviewed Whitehall's contribution as a large employer. All departments have "green ministers" to promote environmentally friendly targets; an employee volunteering scheme extends throughout Whitehall; and 97 per cent of government employees are in workplaces with Investors in People status.\par \par \uc2 Mr Howells has rejected calls for legislation to force companies to introduce social responsibility programmes, arguing that this would lead to many boards meeting only the minimum requirements. But, he said, competitive pressures and the growing interest of investors in companies' reputations would drive such programmes forward. {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.societyandbusiness"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 www.societyandbusiness}}}\uc2 . gov.uk. \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b NS\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 c13 : \uc2 Regulation/Government Policy | c131 : \uc2 Regulatory Bodies | ccat : \uc2 Corporate/Industrial News | eec : \uc2 European Union | gcat : \uc2 Political/Genera