 of good things, it lacked "a fully joined-up strategy".\par \par \uc2 But last night a Tesco spokesman said: "We take \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2  very seriously. We may look at how it's reported."\par \par \uc2 Safeway said there had been "a clerical error" on its part, and fully expected to be included in the index when it was launched.\par \par \uc2 RBS has been excluded on human rights grounds. Mr Mackenzie said RBS operated in countries with a controversial human rights record, therefore "should state clear policies" but so far had not done so. RBS said: "We will sit down with FTSE to talk about this. We believe we're a very ethical operation." Editorial Comment, Page 14 Clear conscience, Page 21 Full details: {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.ftse4good.com"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 www.ftse4good.com}}}\uc2 . \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b CO\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 edlc : \uc2 Safeway PLC | rbsct : \uc2 Royal Bank of Scotland Group PLC | tsco : \uc2 Tesco PLC\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b IN\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 i41 : \uc2 Food/Beverages/Tobacco | i64 : \uc2 Ret