i0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b LP\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Tesco, Safeway and Royal Bank of Scotland were among 36 of Britain's top 100 companies blackballed from a new ethical share index launched on Tuesday.\par \par \uc2 Yet Shell and BP were included in the FTSE4Good indices, produced by the index joint venture between the Financial Times and the London Stock Exchange.\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b TD\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Of the 757 companies in the FTSE All Share, almost two-thirds did not make it, some because of a lack of information rather than positive evidence of unethical practices.\par \par \uc2 Companies involved in tobacco, weapons and nuclear power were excluded. Others were judged on three criteria: the \b \highlight22\uc2 environment\b0 \highlight\uc2 , human rights and social issues, including stakeholder relations.\par \par \uc2 Mark Makepeace, chief executive of FTSE, said Tesco had failed to meet the environmental criteria, adding "if you are a high impact company, then the hurdles are higher".\par \par \uc2 Dr Craig Mackenzie, a member of the FTSE4Good Advisory panel, said that while Tesco had done a lot of good things, it lacked "a fully joined-up strategy".\par \par \uc2 But last night a Tesco spokesman said: "We take \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2  very seriously. We may look at how it's reported."\par \par \uc2 Safeway said there had been "a clerical error" on its part, and fully expected to be included in the index when it was launched.\par \par \uc2 RBS has been excluded on human rights grounds. Mr Mackenzie said RBS operated in countries with a controversial human rights record, therefore "should state clear policies" but so far had not done so. RBS said: "We will sit down with FTSE to talk about this. We believe we're a very ethical operation." Editorial Comment, Page 14 Clear conscience, Page 21 Full details: {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.ftse4good.com"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 www.ftse4good.com}}}\uc2 . \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b CO\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 edlc : \uc2 Safeway PLC | rbsct : \uc2 Royal Bank of Scotland Group PLC | tsco : \uc2 Tesco PLC\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b IN\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 i41 : \uc2 Food/Beverages/Tobacco | i64 : \uc2 Ret