eptable practices. The most recent lesson in this respect has been learnt by Triumph International following its operations in Burma.\par \par \uc2 Please continue to praise companies for charity but do not forget that more serious matters belong under the heading of \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2 .\par \par \uc2 Vidar Lindefjeld, Director, International Social Affairs, Confederation of Norwegian Business and Industry, 0303 Oslo, Norway. \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b NS\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 gcat : \uc2 Political/General News | gcha : \uc2 Charities | ncat : \uc2 Content Types | nlet : \uc2 Letter | nrgn : \uc2 Routine General News\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b RE\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 asiaz : \uc2 Asia | devgcoz : \uc2 Emerging Market Countries | eeurz : \uc2 Central/Eastern Europe | eurz : \uc2 Europe | nordz : \uc2 Nordic Countries | norw : \uc2 Norway | russ : \uc2 Russia | scandz : \uc2 Scandinavia | ussrz : \uc2 CIS Countries | weurz : \uc2 Western Europe\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trle