0\lin0 \uc2 The problem with BAT's report is that it ignores or skates over the most serious impacts of its business.\par \par \uc2 While grudgingly accepting that smoking is associated with "real risks of serious diseases", BAT still denies the harm caused by passive smoking, despite international consensus by cancer experts that passive smoking is a cause of lung cancer and other diseases.\par \par \uc2 We provided written input to the audit but chose not to allow BAT to appropriate our time and resources in a dialogue because we could envisage no useful outcome for public health. Instead we prepared a much more realistic and evidence-based assessment of BAT's impact and this is available at {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.ash.org.uk"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 www.ash.org.uk}}}\par \par \uc2 Clive Bates, Director, Action on Smoking and Health, London EC2A 4HW\par \par \uc2 London Edition 2. \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b CO\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 batin : \uc2 British American Tobacco PLC\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b IN\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 i41 : \uc2 Food/Beverages/Tobacco | i429 : \uc2 Tobacco Products |